biblical evidence suggests that non-theocratic government acts are
evil 90.2%&quot; of the time, theocratic ones are evil 60.3%&quot; of
the time, and overall government acts were evil 78.4%&quot; of the
time.&quot;</FONT></FONT> 
</P>
